Package com.nokia.places.request

The request package provides classes used to create requests to the RESTful Places service.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    CategoryRequest
    This interface represents a query which returns a collection of categories.
    CategoryRequestListener
    This interface is used to provide a set of standard callback methods when making an asynchronous CategoryRequest
    PlaceRequest
    This interface defines a request which is used to obtain in-depth information about a single location.
    PlaceRequestListener
    This interface is used to provide a set of standard callback methods when making an asynchronous PlaceRequest
    Request
    This interface forms the basis of all request classes, and allows the user to cancel asynchronous requests.
    ResultPageRequest
    This interface represents any query which returns places data in the form of a ResultPage.
    ResultPageRequestListener
    This interface is used to provide a set of standard callback methods when making an asynchronous ResultPageRequest
    SuggestionRequest
    This interface represents a request to the suggestions service which offers suggestions to complete a partially entered text.
    SuggestionRequestListener
    This interface is used to provide a set of standard callback methods when making an asynchronous SuggestionRequest
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Modifier
    This class allows a user to modify the responses provided by the requests to the RESTful places service.

Package com.nokia.places.request Description

The request package provides classes used to create requests to the RESTful Places service.

CategoryRequest, PlaceRequest, ResultPageRequest and SuggestionRequest classes may be created by using the PlaceFactory
